OL,3,CMale 'Hoff' crab has bigger claws to
OL,4,Cfight other males for a mate
OL,6,FMale crabs of a species named after
OL,7,FDavid Hasselhoff grow bigger claws
OL,8,Fthan females so they can fight each
OL,9,Fother for a mate, according to a new
OL,10,Fstudy.
OL,12,FScientists from the universities of
OL,13,FPortsmouth and Southampton discovered
OL,14,Fthe difference in claw size while
OL,15,Fmonitoring the "Hoff crab", which
OL,16,Fgained its nickname thanks to its
OL,17,Fhairy chest, prompting comparisons
OL,18,Fwith the Baywatch star.
OL,26,@wD@POUwD@ZO]
