OL,3,CMale 'Hoff' crab has bigger claws to
OL,4,Cfight other males for a mate
OL,6,FDr Nicolai Roterman, a deep-sea
OL,7,Fecologist from the University of
OL,8,FPortsmouth and lead author of the
OL,9,Fstudy published in the journal PLOS
OL,10,FOne, said: "This is the first study to
OL,11,Fshow claw sexual dimorphism in yeti
OL,12,Fcrabs which live exclusively in harsh
OL,13,Fdeep-sea environments like
OL,14,Fhydrothermal vents and methane seeps.
OL,26,@rD@LOU
