OL,3,CMale 'Hoff' crab has bigger claws to
OL,4,Cfight other males for a mate
OL,6,FThe team compared the Hoff crab with
OL,7,Fanother yeti crab, the Kiwa puravida
OL,8,Ffound off Costa Rica, which does not
OL,9,Fshow difference claw sizes between the
OL,10,Fsexes.
OL,12,FDr Roterman said: "This could be
OL,13,Fbecause the Costa Rica yeti crabs may
OL,14,Fbe using their claws ` which are
OL,15,Flonger and hairier than those of the
OL,16,FHoff crab ` primarily for food
OL,17,Fproduction rather than fighting, or
OL,18,Fperhaps there is some other factor at
OL,19,Fplay that we have yet to discover.
OL,26,@tD@SOU
