OL,3,CMale 'Hoff' crab has bigger claws to
OL,4,Cfight other males for a mate
OL,6,F"We don't yet know if these claw sex
OL,7,Fdifferences are the norm for the yeti
OL,8,Fcrab family, or an exception. But the
OL,9,Fdiscovery provides a starting point
OL,10,Ffor future research."
OL,26,@nD@AOUrD@UO]
