OL,3,CMale 'Hoff' crab has bigger claws to
OL,4,Cfight other males for a mate
OL,6,FDr Roterman, who coined the Hoff
OL,7,Fnickname when the species was first
OL,8,Fdiscovered in 2010, added:
OL,9,F"Understanding the physiology,
OL,10,Fbehaviour, ecology and evolution of
OL,11,Fanimals adapted to the most extreme
OL,12,Fconditions give us insights into what
OL,13,Fevolution is capable of, and therefore
OL,14,Fhow life is likely to adapt to a
OL,15,Fwarming planet and other natural and
OL,16,Fhuman-induced ecological stressors."
